Git common day to day process
git status
git add <filenames>
git commit
git push -u origin master


Create a new repository on the command line
touch README.md
git init
git add README.md
git commit -m "first commit"
git remote add origin https://github.com/isaacrael/python.git
git push -u origin master

Push an existing repository from the command line
git remote add origin https://github.com/isaacrael/python.git
git push -u origin master 

Git Clone Operation

git clone https://github.com/isaacrael/python.git python # Adds top level directory called python to your project


Git Fetch Operation 

open git terminal window from application explorer in Aptana
cd to the directory where the project is located
git init
git remote add isaac https://github.com/isaacrael/python.git
git fetch isaac


Git Graphical Interfaces

gitk&

